00:47:14.920 --> 00:47:18.880
we were able to do some spatial transcriptomics and sort of

815
00:47:18.920 --> 00:47:21.840
as a first step confirm, is the drug actually doing what it's supposed to?

816
00:47:21.900 --> 00:47:22.820
Is it hitting its target?

